data.description: Great location, well maintained home, close to Scenic Hwy 124, Stonecrest Mall and Hwy 20. This home features 5 bedrooms, 3 fullbath, formal liv and din, family rm with fire place. Home was just renovated to include a new kit with new appliances, granite counter top and back splash, wood floors throughout main floor and hall way upstairs. Flex room on main floor, can be bedroom, office or library, large master bedroom upstairs with master bath includes, garden tub, saparate shower, private toilet area, dbl vanity and wlk-in-closet. There are 3 large secondary bedrooms upstairs with one full bath, one secondary bedroom has stairs leading to family room, laundry room on main floor, two car garage with remote, mainicured lawn, private backyard with patio. home is move in ready.
